platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Austrian student Klemens Strasser studies computer science at the Technical University of Graz, and Elementary Minute is his first major development project. An absorbing quiz game, it gives you a minute to answer as many true/false questions as you can. If you prefer to take your time, you can try another mode that gives you four chances to get the right answer before the jig is up.
